<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="explosion-n">explosion <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ɪk'spləʊʒn/    美 /ɪk'sploʊʒn/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>爆炸 (声)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The explosion was caused by a burst gas pipe.
这次爆炸是由一条爆裂的煤气管道引起的。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>(感情) 爆发；激增：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a <strong>population explosion</strong>
人口激增</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>an explosion in oil price
油价猛涨</p></div></div>